channel.title: MerakiMusic [Collab?] - I also have FL
channel.description:
I want to make another collab with someone as I haven't made a full on collab in about a year now. I mainly use FL but I can also use Auxy. Also, I mainly make progressive house and future house tracks. Check out my most recent Auxy collab with my friend Jacob Justus and let me know if you wanna collab too! Link to my recent collab: https://open.spotify.com/track/4oUl0Jcd6ZdmG95dN6KRfS?si=tjzEDgehRi-taHRK6b6ZWA
Message me on instagram if you wanna collab @colby.xz
